categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Gumbrak Hoxz was a Jedi Padawan who served the Jedi Order during the Clone Wars. A Mon Calamari male from Dac, he was a contemporary of Tallisibeth Enwandung-Esterhazy. He participated in the 19 BBY Jedi Temple Apprentice Tournament, in which, he was set against fellow apprentice Atresh Pikil in the first round. Apprentice Enwandung-Esterhazy, who was watching from the side-lines, thought that, although he had grown in strength leading up to the tournament, he had yet to adjust to his new size and webbed feet.
